data.description: This is your opportunity to own a luxurious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom retreat, featuring 2138 sqft of living space on a sprawling 1-acre canvas. With the addition of solar panels, this residence is both eco-friendly and primed for your personal touch. Imagine the freedom of a home powered by the sun, and the potential that awaits on this generous acre. Whether you're envisioning a lush garden, a tranquil escape, or a place to entertain under the stars, this property is your canvas.
